OL,3,CArrests made as woman remains in
OL,4,Ccritical condition after stabbing
OL,6,FMultiple arrests have been made
OL,7,Ffollowing a serious attack in
OL,8,FHuddersfield as a woman fights for her
OL,9,Flife in hospital.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to
OL,12,FTopaz Close on Monday 11 May after a
OL,13,F30-year-old woman was stabbed in the
OL,14,Fhead and neck. She remains in hospital
OL,15,Fin a critical condition.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
