OL,3,CArrests made as woman remains in
OL,4,Ccritical condition after stabbing
OL,6,FA 17-year-old boy from Huddersfield
OL,7,Fhas now been arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fattempted murder and three teenagers
OL,9,Ffrom Huddersfield aged, 18, 17 and 16
OL,10,Fhave been arrested on suspicion of
OL,11,Fassisting an offender.
OL,13,FKirklees CID says it is continuing to
OL,14,Fappeal for witnesses to the attack
OL,15,Fwhich took place at around 10.30pm on
OL,16,F11 May.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
