OL,3,CArrests made as woman remains in
OL,4,Ccritical condition after stabbing
OL,6,FPolice also say they want to speak to
OL,7,Fanyone who saw two suspects in the
OL,8,FKirkby and Edgerton area on an E-Bike
OL,9,For a Surron Bike before or after the
OL,10,Fstabbing.
OL,12,FAnyone who can assist enquiries is
OL,13,Fasked to contact police by calling 101.
